        i0.ɵɵtext(244, "\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0If you choose to post messages on Our message boards, chat rooms or other message areas or leave feedback/ service review, We will collect and store such information You provide to Us. Please note such messages posted by You will be in public domain and can be read by others as well, please exercise caution while posting such messages, personal details, and reviews. We retain this information as necessary to resolve disputes, provide customer support, respond to queries, for internal research and troubleshoot problems as permitted by law.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(245, "p")(246, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(247, "3.5)");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(248, "\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0If You send us correspondence, such as emails or letters, or if other users or third parties send us correspondence about Your activities or postings on the Platform, We may collect and retain such information into a file specific to You for responding to Your request and addressing concerns in relation to Your use of the Platform. We shall be entitled to retain Your Personal Information and other information for such duration as may be required for the purposes specified hereunder and will be used only in accordance with this Privacy Policy.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(249, "p")(250, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(251, "3.6)");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(252, "\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0In Our efforts to continually improve Our service offerings, We will occasionally ask you to complete surveys conducted either by us or through a third- party market research agency. These surveys may ask you for personal information, contact information, gender, date of birth, demographic information (like pin code, age, or income level), attributes such as your interests, household or lifestyle information, and other such information that you may choose to provide. Participation in these surveys is purely voluntary in nature. We use this data to tailor your experience at our Platform, providing you with content that we think you might be interested in and to display content according to your preferences.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(253, "p")(254, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(255, "3.7)");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(256, "\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0Use of our Platform is available only to persons who can form a legally binding contract under the Indian Contract Act, 1872. We do not knowingly solicit or collect personal information from children under the age of 18 years. If you have shared any personal information of children under the age of 18 years, you represent that you have the authority to do so and permit us to use the information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd()();
        i0.ɵɵelement(257, "hr", 5);
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(258, "div", 2)(259, "h6");
        i0.ɵɵtext(260, "4.\u00A0\u00A0 Sharing of Your Information :");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelement(261, "br");
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(262, "p")(263, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(264, "4.1)\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0 Third Party Service Providers : ");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(265, "We may disclose Your Personal Information to third party vendors, delivery partners, consultants, partners for carrying out research and other service providers who work for either of Us or provide Services through the Platform and are bound by contractual obligations to keep such Personal Information confidential and use it only for the purposes for which it has been disclosed to them and maintain the same level of data protection that is adhered to by Us. This disclosure may be required, for instance, to provide You access to the Services and process payments including validation of Your Payment Details, to facilitate and assist marketing and advertising activities/initiatives, for undertaking auditing or data analysis, or to prevent, detect, mitigate, and investigate fraudulent or illegal activities related to the Services. You expressly consent to the sharing of Your information with third party service providers, including payment gateways, to process payments and manage Your payment-related information. We do not disclose Your Personal Information to third parties for their marketing and advertising purposes without Your explicit consent.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(266, "p")(267, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(268, "4.2)\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0Compliance with Law : ");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(269, "We may disclose Your information including Personal Information, to the extent necessary: (i) to comply with laws, regulatory requirements and to respond to lawful requests and legal process or an investigation, (ii) to protect Our rights and property, the Users, and others, including to enforce the Terms or to prevent any illegal or unlawful activities, and (iii) in an emergency to protect Our personal safety and assets the Users, or any person. In all such events, We shall in no manner be responsible for informing You or seeking Your approval or consent. We may also share aggregated anonymized (and de-identified) information with third parties at Our discretion.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(270, "p")(271, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(272, "4.3)\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0 Acquisition Sale or Merger : ");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(273, "We may, in compliance with applicable laws, share all Your Personal Information (including Sensitive Personal Information) and other information with any other business entity(ies), in the event of a merger, sale, reorganization, amalgamation, joint ventures, restructuring of business or transfer or disposition of all or any portion of any of Us. Should such a transaction occur, that other business entity (or the new combined entity) will be required to follow this Privacy Policy with respect to Your Personal Information.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(274, "p")(275, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(276, "4.4)\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0 Seamless User Experience : ");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(277, "In the event the license agreement is terminated or the territory of the license is modified or limited in any manner, We may share any or all Your Personal Information (including Sensitive Personal Information, if any) with the incoming licensee for the continuity of smooth operation of the Platform and seamless user experience.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(278, "p")(279, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(280, "4.5)\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(281, "You also specifically agree and consent to Us for collecting, storing, processing, transferring, and sharing information (including Personal Information and Sensitive Personal Information) related to You with third parties such as with entities registered under applicable laws including payment gateways and aggregators, solely for Us to provide Services to You including processing Your transaction requests for the Services or to improve Your experience on the Platform.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd()();
        i0.ɵɵelement(282, "hr", 5);
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(283, "div", 2)(284, "h6");
        i0.ɵɵtext(285, "5.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0Data Security Precautions :");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelement(286, "br");
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(287, "p")(288, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(289, "5.1)");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(290, "\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0 Please be aware that the transmission of information via the internet is not completely secure. Although we will do our best to protect your personal data, we cannot guarantee the security of your data transmitted through the Website. Once we have received your information, we will use strict physical, electronic, and procedural safeguards to try to prevent unauthorized access. We take reasonable precautions and follow industry best practices to protect your Personal Information from loss, misuse, unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction, in compliance with applicable laws.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(291, "p")(292, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(293, "5.2)");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(294, "\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0 We use vault and tokenization services from third party service providers to protect the sensitive personal information provided by you. The third-party service providers with respect to our vault and tokenization services and our payment gateway and payment processing are compliant with the payment card industry standard (generally referred to as PCI compliant service providers). You are advised to not send your full credit/debit card details through unencrypted electronic platforms. You are responsible for keeping the details confidential, where we have given you (or where you have chosen) a username and password which enables you to access certain parts of our Platform. Please be advised to not share your password with anyone including the agents, employees or representatives of CLOREV Laundry.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(295, "p")(296, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(297, "5.3)");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(298, "\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0If you receive an e-mail, a call from a person/association claiming to be from CLOREV Laundry seeking sensitive personal information like debit/credit card PIN, net-banking or mobile banking password, We request you to never provide such information. We at CLOREV Laundry or Our affiliate logistics partner do not at any time connect with you requesting for such information. If you have already revealed such information, report it immediately to an appropriate law enforcement agency.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(299, "p")(300, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(301, "5.4)");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(302, "\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0 Notwithstanding anything contained in this Privacy Policy or elsewhere, CLOREV Laundry shall not be held responsible for:");
        i0.ɵɵelement(303, "br");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(304, "table")(305, "tr")(306, "td", 9);
        i0.ɵɵtext(307, "(i)");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(308, "td", 9);
        i0.ɵɵtext(309, " any security breaches on third-party websites or applications or for any actions of third-parties that receive Your Personal Information; or");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd()();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(310, "tr")(311, "td", 9);
        i0.ɵɵtext(312, "(ii)");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(313, "td", 9);
        i0.ɵɵtext(314, " any loss, damage, or misuse of Your Personal Information, if such loss, damage, or misuse is attributable to a Force Majeure Event. For the purpose of this Privacy Policy, a ");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd()()();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(315, "div", 10);
        i0.ɵɵtext(316, " \u201CForce Majeure Event\u201D shall mean any event that is beyond Our reasonable control and shall include, acts of God, fires, explosions, wars or other hostilities, insurrections, revolutions, strikes, labour unrest, earthquakes, floods, pandemic, epidemics or regulatory or quarantine restrictions, unforeseeable governmental restrictions or controls or a failure by a third party hosting provider or internet service provider or on account of any change or defect in the software and/or hardware of Your computer system. ");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd()();
        i0.ɵɵelement(317, "hr", 5);
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(318, "div", 2)(319, "h6");
        i0.ɵɵtext(320, "6.\u00A0\u00A0 Links to Thired-Party Sites:");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelement(321, "br");
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(322, "p")(323, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(324, "6.1)");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(325, "\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0 Our Platform may contain links to other websites (\u201CThird-Party Sites\u201D). Any personal information about You (including but not limited to, IP address, browser specification, or operating system) collected whilst visiting such websites is not governed by this Policy. We will not be in any manner responsible for and have no control over the practices and content of any Third-Party Site accessed using the links contained on Our Platform. This Privacy Policy shall not apply to any information You may disclose to any of Our service providers/service personnel which We do not require You to disclose to Us or any of Our Service Providers under this Privacy Policy.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(326, "p")(327, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(328, "6.2)");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(329, "\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0We may use third-party advertising companies to serve ads when You visit Our Platform. These companies may use information (not including Your name, address, email address, or telephone number) about Your visits to Our Platform and other websites in order to provide advertisements about goods and services of Your interest. You agree and acknowledge that We are not liable for the information published in search results or by any Third-Party Sites.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd()();
        i0.ɵɵelement(330, "hr", 5);
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(331, "div", 2)(332, "h6");
        i0.ɵɵtext(333, "7.\u00A0\u00A0 Your Consent,Withdrawal and Data retention :");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelement(334, "br");
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(335, "p")(336, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(337, "7.1)\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0 Your Consent : ");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(338, "By visiting our Platform or by providing Your information, You consent to the collection, use, storage, disclosure and otherwise processing of Your information (including sensitive personal information) on the Platform in accordance with this Privacy Policy. All information disclosed by You shall be deemed to be disclosed willingly and without any coercion. We will not be liable to the authenticity, genuineness, misrepresentation, fraud, negligence of the information disclosed nor will We be in any way responsible to verify any information obtained from You. If You disclose to Us any personal information relating to other people, You represent that You have the authority to do so and permit s to use the information in accordance with this Privacy Policy. ");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(339, "p")(340, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(341, "7.2)\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0 Withdrawal of Consent : ");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(342, "You may choose to withdraw Your consent provided hereunder by writing to Grievance Officer (refer clause 8.1) via email with the subject line \u201CWithdrawal of Consent\u201D. Please note, however, that withdrawal of consent will not be retroactive and will be in accordance with this Privacy Policy, related Terms of Use and applicable laws. In the event You withdraw consent given to Us under this Privacy Policy, We reserve the right to restrict or deny the provision of Our Services for which We consider such information to be necessary. ");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(343, "p")(344, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(345, "7.3)\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0 Data Retention : ");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(346, " We retain your personal information for a period no longer than is required for the purpose for which it was collected or as required under any applicable law. However, we may retain data related to you if there is a legal obligation to retain the data; if required to comply with any applicable statutory or regulatory retention requirement by law; if we believe it may be necessary to prevent fraud or future abuse; to enable CLOREV Laundry to exercise its legal rights and/or defend against legal claims; or for other legitimate purposes. We may continue to retain your data in anonymized form for analytical and research purposes.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelement(347, "p");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelement(348, "hr", 5);
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(349, "div", 2)(350, "h6");
        i0.ɵɵtext(351, "8.\u00A0\u00A0 Grievances and Queries:");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelement(352, "br");
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(353, "p")(354, "b");
        i0.ɵɵtext(355, "8.1)");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵtext(356, "\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0If you have any queries, concerns, or complaints in relation to collection or usage of your personal information under this Privacy Policy, please contact our Grievance Officer at details provided below. We shall endeavour to respond promptly, however except where required by law, We cannot ensure a response regarding topics unrelated to this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices.");
        i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(357, "p");
        i0.ɵɵtext(358, " Mr. Sudhir Mishra ");
